ings.builder()'s default for\nrequireProofKey from false to true (PKCE-by-default). DHIS2's existing OAuth2\nclients and the authorization-code flow do not send a PKCE code_challenge, so\nthe new default made /oauth2/authorize fail with invalid_request and bounce the\nbrowser to the redirect_uri (e2e OAuth2Test: net::ERR_CONNECTION_REFUSED, 11\nerrors). Explicitly set requireProofKey(false) in applyCreateDefaults to\npreserve prior (SAS 1.x) behaviour.\n\nSECURITY REVIEW: decide whether to adopt PKCE-by-default for DHIS2 OAuth2\nclients (recommended) and migrate clients/flows accordingly.\n\nVerified: new client stores require-proof-key=false and /oauth2/authorize now\nredirects to /login/ instead of erroring.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"},"id":"8bcbe6325c52aa3a052139f72ef3013c9abbd826","tree_id":"2215d0fa1cf24e03c74b3e189acec8ac603ef6c4","timestamp":"2026-06-02T06:19:14Z","committer":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https: